message.content: cs.AR, cs.AR is the most likely category as the paper proposes new DRAM architectures and mechanisms to reduce DRAM latency, which falls under the domain of computer architecture. Other likely categories could be cs.SY (systems and control), cs.ET (embedded systems), cs.DC (distributed, parallel, and cluster computing), and cs.SE (software engineering) as the proposed mechanisms could have implications in these areas as well.
